1. Get the source code from github:
	git clone https://github.com/ANGSD/tmon 

2. Enter to the Directory:
	cd tmon

3. Make:
	sudo make 

4. Make Install:
	sudo make install

5. Enable Tmon:
	systemctl enable tmond.service
	
6. Copy tmonrc file to /home/user/ as .tmonrc
	sudo copy tmonrc ~/.tmonrc
	
7. Activate Tmon:
	sudo tmond
	
8. edit ~/.tmonrc file
	sudo ~/.tmonrc
		
		Enter the host and port no. (basically 7777) in it: such as:
		
		192.168.22.70	7777
		192.168.22.113	7777

9. Run to monitor:
	tmon -f ~/.tmonrc
	
	
	
	
	






More details: https://github.com/ANGSD/tmon/blob/master/README.md
